        <item>
            <title>Version 0.2.2</title>
            <sparkle:version>0.2.2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 0.2.2</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>New: Gemma 3 4B added as an LLM option</li>
                    <li>New: Auto-classify unknown apps with per-app category overrides in Settings</li>
                    <li>New: Sparkle auto-updater with Check for Updates in About tab</li>
                    <li>New: PostHog analytics (opt-out available in Settings)</li>
                    <li>New: Sentry crash reporting (opt-out available in Settings)</li>
                    <li>New: Liquid glass UI redesign and updated app icon</li>
                    <li>Improved: Prompt quality and LLM cleanup pipeline</li>
                    <li>Fixed: Email formatting structure across all model sizes</li>
                    <li>Fixed: Echo bug in LLM output</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 14:44:08 +0000</pubDate>
