        <item>
            <title>Version 0.2.3</title>
            <sparkle:version>0.2.3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 0.2.3</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>New: Ollama support as an LLM inference backend</li>
                    <li>New: llama.cpp engine with GGUF model support</li>
                    <li>New: KV prompt caching to speed up repeated inference</li>
                    <li>New: Configurable LLM skip-word threshold in Settings</li>
                    <li>New: Externalized per-category prompt rules with Settings UI</li>
                    <li>New: Redesigned Settings, popover, and onboarding UI</li>
                    <li>Improved: STT-to-LLM pipeline performance (emoji short-circuit, BPE cache)</li>
                    <li>Improved: Audio capture and model loading pipeline</li>
                    <li>Fixed: LLM output token cap removed; VAD thresholds corrected</li>
                    <li>Fixed: "Tighten phrasing" rule that caused words to be dropped</li>
                    <li>Fixed: llama.cpp API compatibility and concurrent decode crash</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 08:11:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/sunboy/yapyap/releases/download/v0.2.3/YapYap-v0.2.3.dmg"
