        <item>
            <title>Version 0.2.8</title>
            <sparkle:version>0.2.8</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 0.2.8</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>New: Parakeet TDT v3 is now the default STT model (faster, runs on Apple Neural Engine)</li>
                    <li>New: V2 prompt engine with chat-style multi-turn few-shot examples</li>
                    <li>New: Customizable system prompts and few-shot examples in Settings</li>
                    <li>New: Unified model download service</li>
                    <li>Improved: Paste reliability and onboarding z-order</li>
                    <li>Fixed: Ollama crash on malformed endpoint URL</li>
                    <li>Fixed: llama.cpp crash when prompt exceeds batch size</li>
